Package jot.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoreGameObject
    Abstract class that each generic game object class, each corresponding to a game state, must extend.
    CoreOptions
    Class that sets the default geometry and i/o options.
    ExtensionAIOptions
    Class that sets the default A.I.
    ExtensionGeometryOptions
    Class that sets the default geometry options.
    ExtensionPhysicsOptions
    Class that sets the default physics options.
    FrameworkOptions
    Class that sets the default extras options.
    FrameworkOptions.Options  
    GameObject
    Class that specifies the generic FPS game object, each corresponding to a FPS game state.
